
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
  <head>
    <meta content='text/html; charset=UTF-8' http-equiv='Content-Type' />
  </head>
  <body>
    <h4><center>Your resignation request has been rejected</center> </h4>

<p>This is to inform that the resignation request created by <b><%= @employee_resignation.try(:employee).try(:prefix) %>  <%= @employee_resignation.try(:employee).try(:first_name) %> <%= @employee_resignation.try(:employee).try(:middle_name) %> <%= @employee_resignation.try(:employee).try(:last_name) %>  </b>  on <b> <%= @employee_resignation.try(:resignation_date) %></b>, has been rejected by your reporting manager <b><%= @reporting_master.try(:employee).try(:prefix)%> <%= @reporting_master.try(:employee).try(:first_name)%> <%= @reporting_master.try(:employee).try(:middle_name)%> <%= @reporting_master.try(:employee).try(:last_name)%>.</b></p>

<p>For further details, kindly contact your reporting manager.</p>

<h4>Details of the Resignation:-</h4>

<p>Employee ID:- <%= @employee_resignation.try(:employee).try(:manual_employee_code) %></p>

<p>Employee Name:- <%= @employee_resignation.try(:employee).try(:prefix) %> <%= @employee_resignation.try(:employee).try(:first_name) %> <%= @employee_resignation.try(:employee).try(:middle_name) %> <%= @employee_resignation.try(:employee).try(:last_name) %> </p>

<p>Reason of Separation:- <%= @employee_resignation.try(:reason) %></p>
  </body>
</html>


